一、系统视图下开启dhcp
	 dhcp enable
二、建立dhcp地址池
	ip pool 192.168.1.0wangduan
		network 192.168.1.0 mask 255.255.255.0
		gateway-list 192.168.1.1 
		dns-list 223.5.5.5
		lease day 0 hour 3
	  # 租约
		
	    excluded-ip-address 192.168.1.220 192.168.1.250 # 保留地址
		static-bind ip-address 192.168.1.2 mac-address 5489-984A-3B7B  #为设备 绑定ip地址
三、给端口配置ip地址，并绑定dhcp
		interface g0/0/1
			ip addr 192.168.1.1
			dhcp select global
